    <div class="s-head"><div class="section-icon section-icon--teal rv-scale">⏳</div><div class="s-tag" style="color:var(--sage)">THE TIMING FACTOR</div><h2 class="s-title">Why Filtered Water Matters <em>More</em> at 45+</h2><p class="s-sub">The same contaminants were in your water at 25. Here's why they didn't matter as much then — and why they matter enormously now.</p></div>
    <div class="comparison rv rv-d1">
      <div class="comparison-side comparison-side--good"><span class="comparison-icon" style="animation:float 4s ease-in-out infinite">🌿</span><h4 style="color:var(--sage)">At 25</h4><p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px">Your body compensates naturally</p><ul class="comparison-list"><li>Abundant sebum production</li><li>Peak collagen levels</li><li>Quick acid mantle recovery</li><li>Strong estrogen protection</li><li>Damage rebounds overnight</li></ul></div>
